title: Donald Trump’s campaign prevents Univision news crew from entering Miami rally
text: MIAMI -- Donald Trump's presidential campaign barred a Univision news crew from entering his campaign rally here Friday evening, launching its latest move against the Spanish-language network with which the real estate mogul has feuded this year.
